com.tedros.fxapi.animation

Class BackInterpolator

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.animation.Interpolator
      • com.tedros.fxapi.animation.EasingInterpolator
        • com.tedros.fxapi.animation.BackInterpolator

  • public class BackInterpolator
extends EasingInterpolator
    An interpolator which is also known as the "bow" function. It interpolates shortly below 0 or above 1 and then bows back.

    The following curve illustrates the interpolation.

    The math in this class is taken from http://www.robertpenner.com/easing/.

    Author:
    Christian Schudt

        protected double baseCurve(double v)
        Description copied from class: EasingInterpolator

        Specified by:

        Parameters:
